      • isRecordConvertable

        public boolean isRecordConvertable(java.lang.String record)
        Given an OASIS record string, determines if this converter can actually convert the record to its supported internal object. This checks the record length, the record's identifying date (usually the M0090 date) and the Version indicator. These can be in different offsets in different records.
        Specified by:
